You need to create a function that will be available each time you log in to the system.Within which file should this function be placed?
A)  .bash_profile
B)  .rc
C)  /etc/profile
D)  .bash_run
A
A. The .bash_profile file, if it exists in your home directory, will be executed on login.Note that placing the function in /etc/profile would technically work, but then thefunction would be available to all users, which is not what the question asked for.198Appendix  Answers to the Review Questions8.
